Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.94,0:01:20.92,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fscx85}Ah-ah-ah 群がる視線を抜け
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.14,0:01:21.96,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fscx75}Who's the survivor?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.96,0:01:24.18,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fscx85}勝負は一度きり
